# Client Structure

```
client/
├── app/
│   ├── _layout.tsx          # Root — socket init, call listeners, push setup
│   ├── (main)/              # home, library, profile, friend-requests, etc.
│   └── call/                # outgoing, incoming, pick-song, player, ended
└── src/
    ├── lib/
    │   ├── api.ts           # Axios → SERVER_URL/api
    │   ├── audioPlayer.ts   # Singleton AudioPlayerService (expo-av)
    │   ├── socket.ts        # connectSocket, getSocket, setOnReconnect
    │   ├── call.ts          # initiateCall, acceptCall, registerCallListeners
    │   ├── callSession.ts   # Persists call state (AsyncStorage)
    │   ├── syncEngine.ts    # Sync logic for player screen
    │   └── storage.ts       # JWT in SecureStore
    └── components/
```

## Socket Reconnect (critical on mobile)

- `socket.ts` exposes `setOnReconnect(cb)` — called on every `connect` event
- `_layout.tsx` re-runs `unregisterCallListeners` + `registerCallListeners` on reconnect
- Sockets drop on background/foreground; listeners must be re-registered

## Auth

- JWT stored in SecureStore via `storage.ts`
- On `Invalid token` socket error: clear token, redirect to login
